==製作過程==
「魅力克利夫蘭」是 [[TV_Land|TV Land]]電視台首次自製的情境喜劇(該台過去都只重播其他的影集)，本劇由[[肖恩·海斯|肖恩·海斯]]成立的Hazy Mills製作公司製作，並邀請[[Suzanne_Martin|Suzanne Martin]]擔任編劇。<ref name="THR">{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3iff1c6b7ea787305b7d9468460b01ee6c|title=TV Land picks up 'Hot in Cleveland'|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Nielsen_Business_Media|Nielsen Business Media]]|date=March 1, 2010|accessdate=June 17, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304011252/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/television/news/e3iff1c6b7ea787305b7d9468460b01ee6c|archivedate=2010-03-04}} </ref><ref name="production">{{cite web|url=http://www.inbaseline.com/project.aspx?project_id=206727|title=Hot in Cleveland TV Pilot|work=[[InBaseline|InBaseline]]|publisher=The New York Times Company|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111115232626/http://inbaseline.com/index.aspx|archivedate=2011-11-15|accessdate=June 18, 2010|deadurl=yes}}</ref>本劇使用[[多鏡頭|多鏡頭]]在CBS攝影棚裡在現場觀眾前拍攝而成。<ref name="EW">{{cite news|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/06/17/hot-in-cleveland-attracts-record-ratings-for-tv-land/|title='Hot in Cleveland' attracts record ratings for TV Land|last=Rice|first=Lynette|work=Hollywood Insider|publisher=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''|date=June 17, 2010|accessdate=June 17, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100619005240/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2010/06/17/hot-in-cleveland-attracts-record-ratings-for-tv-land/|archivedate=2010-06-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cleveland.com/tv/index.ssf/2010/06/hot_in_cleveland_embraces_our.html|title='Hot in Cleveland' embraces our fair city instead of bashing it, Valerie Bertinelli says|last=Dawidziak|first=Mark|work=Cleveland.com|publisher=Cleveland Live, Inc|date=June 13, 2010|accessdate=June 18, 2010}}</ref>

TV Land電視台在2010年7月7日宣布續訂第二季，二十集，於2010年11月1日開始製作，並於2011年1月19日首映。<ref name=season2premiere>{{cite news |url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/11/02/tv-lands-hot-in-cleveland-begins-production-on-20-new-episodes-returns-january-19-2011/70446 |title=TV Land's 'Hot In Cleveland," Begins Production on 20 New Episodes; Returns January 19, 2011 |last=Seidman |first=Robert |work=TV By the Numbers |date=November 2, 2010 |accessdate=November 2, 2010}}</ref><ref>[http://blogs.tvland.com/prime/the-betty-white-blitz-hot-in-cleveland-renewed-for-season-2/ "The Betty White Blitz: Hot in Cleveland Renewed for Season 2"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100718090111/http://blogs.tvland.com/prime/the-betty-white-blitz-hot-in-cleveland-renewed-for-season-2/ |date=2010-07-18 }}. [[TV_Land|TV Land]]. July 7, 2010</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://twitter.com/#!/WeLuvBettyWhite/favorites|title='Hot In Cleveland' Season 2 Premiere|date=October 15, 2010|accessdate=October 15, 2010|archive-date=2018-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729201241/https://twitter.com/#!/WeLuvBettyWhite/favorites|dead-url=no}}</ref>在2011年2月28日，TV Land電視台續訂了第三季22集。<ref name=season3renewal>{{cite news |url=http://www.deadline.com/2011/02/tv-land-renews-comedy-hot-in-cleveland-for-third-season/?utm_source=twitterfeed|title=TV Land's 'Hot In Cleveland" Renewed for Third Season|work=Deadline Hollywood |date=February 28, 2011 |accessdate=February 28, 2011}}</ref> 在2011年3月21日，TV Land電視台又宣布第三季追加至24集。<ref name="#1"/> 在2012年1月12日，TV Land電視台續訂了第四季。<ref name="HIC season4"/>

在電視節目專訪上，[[貝蒂‧懷特|貝蒂‧懷特]]透露她原本只出現在首集，但是後來被邀請參與固定角色。有報導指出貝蒂一集的薪水為七萬五千元美金。<ref name=futon>{{cite news|url=http://tv.gawker.com/5611209/how-much-do-your-favorite-tv-stars-get-paid/|title=How much do your favorite TV stars get paid?|publisher=GAWKER TV|date=August 12, 2010|accessdate=August 12, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820034416/http://tv.gawker.com/5611209/how-much-do-your-favorite-tv-stars-get-paid|archivedate=2010年8月20日}}</ref>

==評論==
本劇播出後受到好評，[[溫蒂·馬立克|溫蒂·馬立克]]的表演也受到讚揚。在知名評論網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上，第一季的分數是65分。(滿分100分)<ref>[http://www.metacritic.com/tv/hot-in-cleveland Hot in Cleveland: Season 1]</ref>

===與黃金女郎相比===
由於貝蒂·懷特曾經在1980年代的知名電視影集[[黃金女郎|黃金女郎]]演出過，因此本劇也被認為參考黃金女郎。[[今天_(NBC)|今天_(NBC)]]的 Craig Berman 曾評論本劇「相當接近過去貝蒂懷特在1980年代的知名作品，『黃金女郎』。TV Land 電視台知道要是讓現在的人看那些過去小時候看的影集大概會睡著，因此給予本劇新型態的經典作品。」<ref>{{cite web|author=Craig Berman|title='Cleveland' puts modern twist on 'Golden Girls'|publisher=''[[Today_(NBC_program)|Today]]''|date=July 13, 2010|accessdate=April 2, 2011}}</ref> [[紐約時報|紐約時報]]的 Alessandra Stanley 則評論：「這是 TV Land 首次自製的情境喜劇，並不會很意外看到其他戲劇的影子，「魅力克利夫蘭」有一點[[歡樂酒店|歡樂酒店]]、[[歡樂一家親|歡樂一家親]]，有一點[[黃金女郎|黃金女郎]]」。<ref>{{cite news|author=Alessandra Stanley|title=Hot in Cleveland|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/06/16/arts/television/16hot.html|publisher=''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]''|date=June 15, 2010|accessdate=April 2, 2011}}</ref> {{link-en|The Village Voice|The Village Voice}}的{{link-en|Michael Musto|Michael Musto}}則認為[[溫蒂·馬立克|溫蒂·馬立克]]基本上就是當代的「[[比特里斯·亚瑟|比特里斯·亚瑟]]」。而[[凡萊麗·柏帝內|凡萊麗·柏帝內]]就是新的貝蒂懷特。<ref>{{cite web|author=Michael Musto|title=Hot in Cleveland Is the New Golden Girls|url=http://blogs.villagevoice.com/dailymusto/2010/06/hot_in_clevelan.php|publisher=''[[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]]''|date=June 24, 2010|accessdate=June 2, 2011|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516205837/http://blogs.villagevoice.com/dailymusto/2010/06/hot_in_clevelan.php|archivedate=2011年5月16日}}</ref>

